Located in the heart of Temecula Wine Country in the desirable neighborhood of Chantamar Estates Villas! Truly an entertainer's paradise offering an expansive and private backyard with no neighbors behind, sparkling pool with slide and spa, built-in BBQ, covered patio, game room, and relaxing balcony to enjoy stunning sunsets and mountain views! Highlights include stylish modern upgrades throughout, solar energy system, custom paint, wood-like floors, open concept kitchen with granite counters and oversized eat-in center island overlooking family room, spacious master suite with spa-like bathroom and balcony overlooking mountains, entry level bedroom with bathroom, backyard paradise and so much more!

LOCATION, GUEST HOUSE, POOL & SPA ... This stunning Chante mar Estate home sits on a 1/2 acre of lush landscaping in one of the most desired neighborhoods in Temecula. The main house boasts an open floor plan with 5 bedrooms & 4 bathrooms while the detached guest house has 1 bedroom & 1 bathroom. This upgraded home includes travertine floors, new carpet, wood tile flooring upstairs, plantation shutters, whole house fan, a downstairs bedroom w/ end-suite bathroom, large bedrooms, and a loft.  The open concept kitchen includes granite counters, stainless steel appliances, dual ovens, plenty of storage space, a large island, and a separate breakfast nook. The master suite includes a large bedroom with retreat and a fireplace. The spacious master bath includes a large soaking tub and separate shower, dual walk-in closets with one of the closets built as a safe room (with steel lined interior walls and a steel door). If you enjoy spending time outdoors this backyard is for you. The backyard is complete with a large pebble-Tec pool & spa with a rock water slide & waterfall. The backyard also has a great entertaining area complete with an outdoor kitchen, fireplace, & fire pit. Have kids...this yard is also complete with a custom built playhouse.  Need a large garage...this home has an attached 840 sq. Ft. garage!! Looking for a home with tons of amenities in a prime location with No HOA and Low Taxes...Look no further...you have found it.

Resort style pool home with spa, waterslide, waterfall, and firepit.  Newer roof, windows, and paint.  Remodeled kitchen, updated bathrooms, and much more. Prime location within a quiet cul-de-sac in this desirable Temecula neighborhood with low taxes and no HOA.  One bedroom downstairs (currently used as an office).  Large formal living room, spacious family room with fireplace, and nicely updated kitchen.  Outdoor kitchen, covered patio, and $100,000+ custom rock saltwater pool with steps leading to elevated seating area with unobstructed views.  Three car garage has a single car door at the rear of the garage that could be ideal for storing additional toys or simply using as a pull through to detail your car, motorcycle, etc while you enjoy the sights and sounds of the three separate waterfalls within the pool.  Spacious master suite with expansive walk-in closet.  Large guest bedrooms upstairs.  Large laundry room just off the garage with ample cabinet space and convenient side door leading toward the pool.  Low maintenance, drought tolerant landscape in the rear yard.

Lovely Redhawk pool and spa home on a cul-de-sac street, and with no rear neighbors, it has the WOW factor! Low maintenance yard with 3 hole artificial turf putting green, and inviting swimming pool and spa in the backyard! No HOA! Beautiful darker laminate wood flooring is throughout most of the downstairs giving this home a warm & inviting feel. A great open layout includes a downstairs bedroom and bathroom. Beautiful white cabinets are offset by solid surface counters in the kitchen, an eat at island w/ room for barstool seating and walk in pantry. Adjacent is a large great room open to the kitchen w/fireplace and ceiling fan. Master bathroom has dual mirrored  closets, one a walk in closet, separate sinks and vanity area, tile flooring & a separate soaking tub & shower. The two additional bedrooms upstairs feature walk in closets and a Jack and Jill bathroom! Additionally the upstairs features a built in desk area with cabinetry and open loft area with book case.  Enjoy the beautiful Temecula days & evenings in your backyard with no rear neighbors, while enjoying your lovely pool and spa. Located in the boundaries of excellent South Temecula schools, Redhawk golf course & Temecula's  Wine Country! This truly is a home you can't miss and it can be yours just in time for Summer!
